      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BRETT KEEPING (1) was strongly fancied latest and proved too good with a 2 length win at this track in a handy 22.89. Has the coveted inside box and has a good record over this journey. Great chance to get the job done again. MAXIMUS MERIDIUS (7) has a strong record this track and trip with four wins and four placings from nine starts. In the money last time at this track (23.00) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 4 length second. Among the main chances. SAMMY MY BOY (3) is going well, finishing in the placings twice in a row. Not beaten far last time when a 1.75 lengths second (19.69) in a Mix 1/2/3 at Gunnedah.",
